                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>
                    <persName corresp="#p_DULLESJF1">Dulles</persName> and Mendès-France held a
                    conversation concerning leadership problems in Indochina on October 3,
                    presumably following the signing ceremonies for the Nine-Power Conference.
                        <persName corresp="#p_DULLESJF1">Dulles</persName>’ memorandum of this
                    conversation is printed in <ref target="frus1952-54v13p2#pg_2115">volume XIII,
                        Part 2, page 2115</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
